{"tid":2234892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 有無人ig試過被鎖定左","createTime":"2020-10-08T08:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T20:25:18.000Z","uid":136345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65402391a4cde20fb1ef8a672df890677c3eb671","tid":2234892,"uid":136345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"前排上星期五重好地地 但第二日就話個ac鎖定左login唔到 我懷疑係因為我電腦同電話同時開住ig 攪到佢以為我比人hack 所以鎖左我<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢叫我要用登記ig既email address 去拎返安全碼解鎖返 <a href=\"http://但個陣係yahoo.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%86%E5%80%8B%E9%99%A3%E4%BF%82yahoo.com.hk&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=5b92e91b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">但個陣係yahoo.com.hk</a> 重要幾年無登入過所以自動del左 <a href=\"http://宜家得返yahoo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%AE%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%BE%97%E8%BF%94yahoo.com&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=5a11e7d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">宜家得返yahoo.com</a> 問過yahoo 客服又話已經搵唔返個帳號<br />\n<br />\n好啦跟住我email 去ig個個客戶centre講啦 講撚晒個情況比佢知 <a href=\"http://但佢死地死都要我用yahoo.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%86%E4%BD%A2%E6%AD%BB%E5%9C%B0%E6%AD%BB%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%88%91%E7%94%A8yahoo.com.hk&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=5770cfa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">但佢死地死都要我用yahoo.com.hk</a> 個個號黎覆佢地 講左10幾次話已經比人del左有無其他方法用 講極都唔明 再同佢講佢又唔理我 呢個星期係咁無限loop 點求佢地都無撚用 <br />\n<br />\n有無人知解決辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928d53c821cab7788b0e75fa78ff65b6306be15c","tid":2234892,"uid":136345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:41:02.000Z","msg":"推 有無人知點攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa6a01748ff112fabc6afb74bdeb05f55b3af41","tid":2234892,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10